        <Parent_String>watercraft components [300212614], vehicle components by vehicle type [300244352], vehicle components [300178758], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
